title: Ash above Ubinas Volcano
description: A pale ash plume extended southeastward from Peru’s Ubinas Volcano on May 15, 2014. The natural-color image was acquired by the Advanced Land Imager (ALI) on the Earth Observing-1 (EO-1) satellite.
